OL,3,CAlderney headteacher to retire after
OL,4,Cnearly four decades in education
OL,6,FThe headteacher of St Anne's School in
OL,7,FAlderney will retire at the end of the
OL,8,Facademic year after nearly four
OL,9,Fdecades working in education.
OL,11,FWendy Wilson began her career in
OL,12,Fschools in the late 1980s and taught
OL,13,FEnglish before moving into senior
OL,14,Fleadership.
OL,16,FShe started at St Anne's as Acting
OL,17,FDeputy Head in 2016, gaining the
OL,18,Fposition permanently at the start of
OL,19,F2017 and then becoming headteacher in
OL,20,FMay 2022.
