OL,4,Cnearly four decades in education
OL,6,FMrs Wilson will take early retirement
OL,7,Fin August, following what the States
OL,8,Fof Guernsey call "a long and
OL,9,Fdistinguished career".
OL,11,FKim Hutchison, Head of Primary
OL,12,FLeadership and Development, adds: "We
OL,13,Fare immensely grateful for the
OL,14,Fleadership, care and commitment she
OL,15,Fhas shown throughout her time at the
OL,16,Fschool.
OL,18,F"During her tenure as headteacher, Mrs
OL,19,FWilson has led the school with warmth,
OL,20,Fintegrity and a strong focus on the
OL,21,Fwellbeing and success of every child.
