OL,3,CAlderney headteacher to retire after
OL,4,Cnearly four decades in education
OL,6,F"Mrs Wilson leaves behind a positive
OL,7,Fand lasting legacy for the whole
OL,8,Fschool community."
OL,10,FMrs Wilson says she has made the
OL,11,Fdecision to be able to spend more time
OL,12,Fwith friends and family.
OL,14,FShe explains: "I feel deeply thankful
OL,15,Ffor the privilege of working alongside
OL,16,Fa fabulous staff team and so many
OL,17,Fgenerations of our wonderful school
OL,18,Fcommunity.
