OL,3,CAlderney headteacher to retire after
OL,4,Cnearly four decades in education
OL,6,F"It has been an honour to play even a
OL,7,Fsmall part in their learning journeys
OL,8,Fand personal growth.
OL,10,F"Now that Alderney is truly my home, I
OL,11,Flook forward to watching our island's
OL,12,Fyoung people continue to thrive and
OL,13,Fflourish - this time from the gentler
OL,14,Fperspective of someone enjoying a well-
OL,15,Fearned and leisurely retirement when
OL,16,Fthat chapter arrives."
